OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FVery
OL,6,Fhot and sunny again Thursday, likely
OL,7,Fslightly hotter than Wednesday. Hot
OL,8,Fagain Friday with long sunny periods,
OL,9,Fthough thundery showers may develop.
OL,10,FPerhaps turning cooler with showers
OL,11,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
